You placed the second and the third videos inside a div container that contains the fist one `div.col-md-12`. Each element with class `col-md-12` adds a new padding from the left and right. Simply move place each video container as a siblings (without nesting).

Now you have the structure that looks as follows:
```
&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12&quot;&gt;
 Video 1
